00:24:55,826 --> 00:24:58,028
Yes, ma'am. Right over yonder.

496
00:24:58,128 --> 00:25:01,073
Get the directions here.
I got me to pee.

497
00:25:05,036 --> 00:25:06,637
Got to pee. Hell...

498
00:25:08,874 --> 00:25:10,112
What the...

