00:26:02,093 --> 00:26:04,173
I don't like this.
Go knock on the door.

512
00:26:05,763 --> 00:26:08,467
- Thanks a lot.
- What you worried about, son?

513
00:26:08,567 --> 00:26:10,535
Somebody got to
live to tell the story.

