559
00:28:37,424 --> 00:28:39,627
Yeah, but you still
gotta be careful...

560
00:28:39,728 --> 00:28:42,364
because that could lead to cancer.

561
00:28:42,463 --> 00:28:44,932
Everything don't lead to cancer,
Eileen. Lord, help her.

562
00:28:45,032 --> 00:28:47,434
I'm gonna open the door.
Y'all need fresh air up in here.

563
00:28:47,535 --> 00:28:49,971
Got all these animals. This is
a nice room. I'll stay in here.

564
00:28:50,070 --> 00:28:51,439
- Good, good, good.
- Sure.

565
00:28:51,538 --> 00:28:53,974
Lacey, you do not
have a Christmas tree?

566
00:28:54,075 --> 00:28:55,544
- No, I don't.
- Oh, my God.

567
00:28:55,644 --> 00:28:58,646
- That's why you wanted me to come here.
- Yeah, that's exactly why.

568
00:28:58,747 --> 00:29:00,382
- I'm gonna take this room.
- Okay.

569
00:29:00,481 --> 00:29:01,817
- Okay?
- That's nice too.

570
00:29:01,916 --> 00:29:03,518
- That's a nice room.
- Thank you.

571
00:29:03,617 --> 00:29:06,520
- Is this one yours, Madea?
- Yeah, put it in the room on the end.

572
00:29:06,621 --> 00:29:08,222
- I'm staying down there.
- All right.

573
00:29:08,323 --> 00:29:10,057
- All right.
- Is this your room here?

574
00:29:10,157 --> 00:29:12,426
- It's my room.
- It's lovely.

575
00:29:12,527 --> 00:29:14,195
Thank you. It's not clean.

576
00:29:14,296 --> 00:29:16,397
- Okay, now where's the kitchen?
- Let's go that way.

577
00:29:16,498 --> 00:29:18,133
- It's in there. Go ahead.
- I'm comin'.

578
00:29:18,232 --> 00:29:20,101
Don't be pushing on me.

579
00:29:20,201 --> 00:29:22,537
We saw this. This is the
