to keep an eye on you.

655
00:33:00,154 --> 00:33:03,357
Now, you know what to do and
you know how to behave, right?

656
00:33:03,458 --> 00:33:04,992
Yes, ma'am.

657
00:33:05,093 --> 00:33:07,461
- I'll be right back. Thanks, Madea.
- Yeah, I love it.

658
00:33:07,561 --> 00:33:10,097
I love well-behaved children.
That's wonderful.

659
00:33:10,198 --> 00:33:11,935
Y'all look so nice.

660
00:33:17,805 --> 00:33:21,209
Hello. Hello. Now, y'all got to
go back to the Stepford children.

661
00:33:21,308 --> 00:33:24,878
Don't act like you... Don't act
like this. Now, calm the hell down.

662
00:33:24,979 --> 00:33:28,615
I'm in here. Do yourself a favor.
Do the right thing.

663
00:33:28,715 --> 00:33:31,219
- You belong in this class?
- Yes, ma'am.

664
00:33:31,318 --> 00:33:33,855
- Okay. What's your name?
- Bailey.

665
00:33:33,954 --> 00:33:35,522
Bailey? Okay. Well, go on.

666
00:33:35,623 --> 00:33:38,692
