1416
01:10:03,645 --> 01:10:05,225
I understand.

1417
01:10:08,650 --> 01:10:11,020
You believe that? Sheldon.

1418
01:10:11,121 --> 01:10:13,029
This is a hell of a mess.

1419
01:10:23,265 --> 01:10:25,403
