1460
01:12:32,962 --> 01:12:34,930
- That's what she wanna know.
- Get outta here!

1461
01:12:35,030 --> 01:12:37,000
Heavens no. Why would she...

1462
01:12:37,100 --> 01:12:39,868
- Buddy, the other night with the sheet.
